Ben's number, though.

177
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,916
(whispers):
Okay.

178
00:07:28,949 --> 00:07:32,620
Oh, gosh, it's hard enough
just to scratch your own back.

179
00:07:35,523 --> 00:07:39,627
Right, it's okay, it's okay, you
can call off the search party.

180
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,562
I'm unharmed.

181
00:07:44,297 --> 00:07:45,933
(exhales)

182
00:07:45,966 --> 00:07:48,536
(grunting in pain)
'Sup, wimp?

183
00:07:48,569 --> 00:07:51,071
