I am so sorry.

184
00:07:51,104 --> 00:07:53,006
You must have been
so worried in my absence.

185
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,241
Your absence? I saw
you two days ago.

186
00:07:54,274 --> 00:07:56,710
I thought you were just avoiding
meeting the new lieutenant.

187
00:07:56,744 --> 00:07:58,546
New who? Never mind,
I don't care.

188
00:07:58,579 --> 00:08:00,648
