215
00:08:50,898 --> 00:08:53,266
Well, I don't
see anything.

216
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:55,035
What? I...

217
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:58,606
Ah! Ha-ha! Footprints.

218
00:08:58,639 --> 00:09:00,140
Those are mine.

219
00:09:00,173 --> 00:09:01,609
Oh. Well...

220
00:09:01,642 --> 00:09:03,744
well, then the wind
must have blown

221
00:09:03,777 --> 00:09:05,245
